{"tid":832574,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張學友開騷無人機突襲　警方出大炮擊落","createTime":"2018-09-23T00:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T10:07:07.000Z","uid":3506,"like":212,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7b04827c08dedc8049180b6e11779dfcf1d5e7","tid":832574,"uid":3506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"「歌神」張學友本月21日晚在四川遂寧舉行演唱會期間，現場警方發現有兩部非法無人機在上空盤旋，懷疑有人在偷拍演唱會，鍳於演唱會觀眾人數多，為免傷及無辜，警方隨即使用如「大炮」的反無人機裝置，擊退一部，並逼降另一部，案件仍在調查階段。據知其中一部無人機在演唱會的斜上方攝錄，當時下面没有群眾，符合逼降條件，終成功將無人機逼降並暫扣。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180922/mobile/bkn-20180922201209833-0922_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180922%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180922201209833-0922_00862_001.html&d=Cm9JkcgwGsQCfMRfwXAbXQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0a05d4b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180922/mobile/bkn-20180922201209833-0922_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d610e466773d900f6d0704fc13e4543fb73274","tid":832574,"uid":132587,"like":489,"dislike":1,"score":488,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"張學友d演唱會好似開唔完咁<br />\n前排先有新聞 話有個被通輯既男人入去睇張學友比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ce4d318d1183070c08d7785c4aa5d8e72e1883","tid":832574,"uid":55310,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"為左睇張學友演唱會，可以去到幾盡"},{"pid":"3220b70556bfcdd5c8ce4a5b574c750674b83b9b","tid":832574,"uid":89931,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10635ffcc2fb08a719d1a26e53436c37c0e001e7","tid":832574,"uid":119135,"like":270,"dislike":3,"score"